# PigeonsAI SDK

PigeonsAI python client

## Installation

To install the PigeonsAI SDK, use pip:

```
pip install pigeonsai
```

## Contributing

If you'd like to contribute to the PigeonsAI SDK, please submit a pull request or open an issue on the GitHub repository.
